quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,98,"Qala hatha rahmatun minrabbee fa-itha jaa waAAdu rabbee jaAAalahu dakkaawakana waAAdu rabbee haqqa"
  18,99,"Watarakna baAAdahum yawma-ithinyamooju fee baAAdin wanufikha fee assoorifajamaAAnahum jamAAa"
  18,100,"WaAAaradna jahannama yawma-ithinlilkafireena AAarda"
  18,101,"Allatheena kanat aAAyunuhumfee ghita-in AAan thikree wakanoo layastateeAAoona samAAa"
  18,102,"Afahasiba allatheena kafarooan yattakhithoo AAibadee min doonee awliyaainna aAAtadna jahannama lilkafireena nuzula"
  18,103,"Qul hal nunabbi-okum bil-akhsareenaaAAmala"
  18,104,"Allatheena dalla saAAyuhumfee alhayati addunya wahum yahsaboonaannahum yuhsinoona sunAAa"
  18,105,"Ola-ika allatheena kafaroobi-ayati rabbihim waliqa-ihi fahabitataAAmaluhum fala nuqeemu lahum yawma alqiyamatiwazna"
  18,106,"Thalika jazaohum jahannamubima kafaroo wattakhathoo ayateewarusulee huzuwa"
  18,107,"Inna allatheena amanoowaAAamiloo assalihati kanat lahumjannatu alfirdawsi nuzula"
  18,108,"Khalideena feeha layabghoona AAanha hiwala"
  18,109,"Qul law kana albahru midadanlikalimati rabbee lanafida albahru qabla an tanfadakalimatu rabbee walaw ji/na bimithlihi madada"
  18,110,"Qul innama ana basharunmithlukum yooha ilayya annama ilahukum ilahunwahidun faman kana yarjoo liqaa rabbihifalyaAAmal AAamalan salihan wala yushrikbiAAibadati rabbihi ahada"
